 <text id="F3010T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus reports that his head wound has not yet healed.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-03-05">March the 5th 1864</date>
      <name type="place">
       <orig reg="Jacksonville">Jackson vill</orig>
       <lb/>
       <orig reg="Florida">florady</orig>
       <orig reg="Headquarters">Head quatters</orig>
      </name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p><orig reg="My">Mi</orig> Dear i <orig reg="receive">receve</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> kind and <orig reg="affectionate">a fetchnet</orig> Wife i <orig
      reg="receive">receve</orig> it this night With the <orig reg="greatest">grates</orig> of <orig
      reg="pleasure">pleaser</orig>
     <unclear>kines</unclear>
     <orig reg="my">mi</orig> Dear i am happy to hear that you have <orig reg="such">south</orig>
     good <orig reg="health">healte</orig> i am happy to say thank god that i have had good <orig
      reg="health">healte</orig> so far <orig reg="my">mi</orig> head is not <orig reg="healed"
      >heale</orig>
     <orig reg="up">oup</orig> yet but i <orig reg="Don't">Dont</orig> think that I Will get <orig
      reg="any">eney</orig>
     <orig reg="Cold">Cole</orig> in it <orig reg="for">fer</orig> the <orig reg="Weather"
     >Wether</orig> is <orig reg="pretty">putty</orig> hot <orig reg="here">hear</orig> and has
      <orig reg="been">bean</orig> hot ever since i <orig reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="been">bean</orig> in the south <orig reg="there">thear</orig> is <orig reg="please"
      >pleas</orig> to <orig reg="excuse">excus</orig> this bad <orig reg="writing">riten</orig> and
     the <orig reg="mistake">mastake</orig> i Was <orig reg="writing">riten</orig> i that that i
      <orig reg="only">onely</orig> had one <orig reg="sheet">sheat</orig> of paper and <orig
      reg="When">Whean</orig> I <orig reg="found">fond</orig> out <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i Was
      <orig reg="writing">riten</orig>
     <orig reg="two">too</orig>
     <orig reg="sheet">seate</orig> of <orig reg="paper">pap</orig> and i <orig reg="know"
     >now</orig> that you <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="have">haft</orig> to <orig reg="laugh">lafte</orig>
     <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> got it and <orig reg="look">loke</orig> at it i Will give you the
      <orig reg="right">rit</orig> Direct how to <orig reg="write">rite</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letters you <orig reg="must">mus</orig> Direct <orig reg="your"
     >yor</orig> letter to me</p>

    <p>i am going to rit it on hear</p>

    <closer>
     <salute/>
     <signed>David Demus</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">Co. K 54 Mass.<lb/>volintears </seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
